{"tid":2007964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國副總統彭斯一名助手確診武肺","createTime":"2020-05-08T16:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T04:30:52.000Z","uid":95138,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa313d6e7dfc42b4d01b1dfdaf08e32e9c5eeb8","tid":2007964,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaa6465ce1ab8632d452c3b98b53d1465a1c0cd","tid":2007964,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"Vice President Mike Pence staffer tests positive for coronavirus<br />\n<br />\nWASHINGTON &mdash; An aide to Vice President Mike Pence has tested positive for coronavirus, a senior administration official confirmed to NBC News on Friday.<br />\n<br />\nThe confirmation comes a day after news broke that President Donald Trump&rsquo;s personal valet had also tested positive.<br />\n<br />\nA spokeswoman for Pence did not immediately respond to CNBC&rsquo;s request for comment.<br />\n<br />\nPence was scheduled to travel to Des Moines, Iowa, in the morning, but his departure from Andrews Air Force Base was delayed by nearly an hour as staff dealt with news of the diagnosis. Reporters traveling with Pence said several staffers disembarked from Air Force Two just before takeoff.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/05/08/vice-president-mike-pence-staffer-tests-positive-for-coronavirus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F05%2F08%2Fvice-president-mike-pence-staffer-tests-positive-for-coronavirus.html&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=eede3f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/05/08/vice-president-mike-pence-staffer-tests-positive-for-coronavirus.html</a>"},{"pid":"db323426b8446ce48a325bd708f9c1f30de513a8","tid